{"id":487,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":88,"title":"88. A Coincidence","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence.487/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence-2022-03-07-21-34-43/0-88-a-coincidence.mp3","transcript":"Teresa! What a surprise! What are you doing here?\nTimothy! I don't believe it!\nI'm going to see my daughter. She will marry this weekend. How about you?\nI'm going to visit my parents.\nWhen is your daughter's wedding?\nSunday.\nWow! This Sunday is the 45th wedding anniversary of their wedding, too.\nThis is a surprise!\nAnyway, where is your train leaving from?\nMy train leaves from Platform 3, over there.\nHow long will you...\nNow leaving from Platform 3, train for Vancouver.\nThat's my train. I have to run. Sorry we didn't get more time to talk.\nThat's OK. I'll see you when you get back.\nHave a good time, and say congratulations to your parents!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:49:07","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Teresa! What a surprise! What are you doing here?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence-2022-03-07-21-34-43/1.mp3","time_start":2.01,"time_end":5.5},{"position":2,"content":"Timothy! I don't believe it!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence-2022-03-07-21-34-43/2.mp3","time_start":5.5,"time_end":7.8},{"position":3,"content":"I'm going to see my daughter. She will marry this weekend. How about you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence-2022-03-07-21-34-43/3.mp3","time_start":7.8,"time_end":11.25},{"position":4,"content":"I'm going to visit my parents.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence-2022-03-07-21-34-43/4.mp3","time_s