ent":"That's OK. I'll see you when you get back.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence-2022-03-07-21-34-43/14.mp3","time_start":35.08,"time_end":37.32},{"position":15,"content":"Have a good time, and say congratulations to your parents!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/88-a-coincidence-2022-03-07-21-34-43/15.mp3","time_start":37.32,"time_end":40.37}]}